WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 38]

03:00.960 --> 03:02.360
Jing Yuan, the Demon Lord,

03:02.610 --> 03:04.220
has actually reappeared in the world.

03:05.370 --> 03:07.020
So Fan Yue

03:07.090 --> 03:08.740
actually has the Divine Mantle of the Demon Lord.

03:10.670 --> 03:11.920
Those who hurt her

03:12.630 --> 03:14.120
and want to hurt her

03:15.090 --> 03:16.410
will all die.

03:24.790 --> 03:25.790
No.

03:44.620 --> 03:46.970
You used a self-destructive method to damage the Hidden Heart

03:47.770 --> 03:50.020
and hurt yourself so badly.

03:50.140 --> 03:51.670
You've lost all the power of the Five Contemplations,

03:51.700 --> 03:53.540
and all your meridians are damaged.

03:53.560 --> 03:55.260
You really don't care about your life.

03:55.840 --> 03:57.110
As long as I'm here,

03:57.620 --> 03:58.940
I won't let you

03:59.870 --> 04:01.520
die again.

04:08.210 --> 04:10.380
They say there are no deities left in this world.

04:10.410 --> 04:11.880
But unexpectedly,

04:11.910 --> 04:13.230
the Divine Mantles

04:13.280 --> 04:15.390
of the three Supreme Deities still exist.

04:15.680 --> 04:17.980
And now, the Demon Lord has suddenly returned.

04:18.010 --> 04:19.680
It seems everything has its own fate.

04:20.180 --> 04:21.589
Nothing is absolute.

04:21.620 --> 04:22.940
Indeed.

04:22.970 --> 04:25.720
We tried to bring down Bai Shuo,

04:25.740 --> 04:28.520
but today, it was Bai Shuo who saved us all.

04:28.640 --> 04:30.480
And who could have imagined

04:30.510 --> 04:33.190
that Chong Zhao, the boy we raised ourselves,

04:33.250 --> 04:34.980
has the Divine Mantle of the Hidden Lord?

04:36.690 --> 04:39.210
Although the Hidden Heart was severely damaged by Bai Shuo,

04:39.800 --> 04:41.960
Zhen Yu took it away

04:41.990 --> 04:43.230
along with Chong Zhao.

04:43.250 --> 04:46.330
If the Hidden Lord truly returns,

04:46.350 --> 04:47.960
the Eternal Sects will be in peril,

04:47.990 --> 04:49.470
and so will all living beings.

04:51.980 --> 04:53.090
High Eternals,

04:53.110 --> 04:55.400
are we just going to sit and do nothing?

04:55.430 --> 04:57.230
The Eternals exist to protect the world.

04:57.250 --> 04:59.080
These aren't just empty words.

04:59.110 --> 05:00.230
If Chong Zhao

05:00.460 --> 05:02.020
truly becomes the Hidden Lord,

05:03.000 --> 05:04.400
we, the four High Eternals of Lanling,

05:04.420 --> 05:07.020
will unite the full strength of the Eternals

05:07.050 --> 05:07.930
to kill him.

05:09.330 --> 05:11.060
That's easy for you to say.

05:11.090 --> 05:12.730
That's a deity.

05:12.750 --> 05:13.920
How do we kill him?

05:13.950 --> 05:15.140
If you're so afraid of dying,

05:15.160 --> 05:16.280
you can just

05:16.310 --> 05:17.630
find a cave and hide.

05:17.650 --> 05:20.330
High Eternal Jing Lei, you speak so righteously now,

05:20.360 --> 05:21.650
but Lanling

05:21.670 --> 05:22.780
still owes everyone

05:22.830 --> 05:24.710
an explanation as to what Jin Yao did.

05:24.740 --> 05:25.910
Indeed.

05:25.950 --> 05:27.830
Jin Yao is the sect leader of Lanling,

05:27.860 --> 05:29.690
yet for his own personal gain,

05:29.710 --> 05:31.550
he brutally killed Eternal disciples.

05:31.580 --> 05:33.990
Lanling must give us an explanation.

05:34.010 --> 05:34.920
Otherwise,

05:34.950 --> 05:38.560
how can it continue to be the head of the Eternal Sects?

05:39.030 --> 05:40.470
-Well,
-You...

05:41.190 --> 05:42.630
Lanling will look into

05:42.650 --> 05:44.980
Jin Yao's crimes.

05:45.000 --> 05:47.320
But tell me, are you blaming us

05:47.350 --> 05:49.960
to seek justice for the victimized Eternals

05:49.980 --> 05:51.659
or to become the new head of the Eternals?

05:51.690 --> 05:53.610
Virtue unfit for status invites disaster.

05:53.630 --> 05:54.710
Shouldn't Lanling take responsibility

05:54.740 --> 05:55.860
for what Jin Yao did?

05:55.880 --> 05:57.050
Lanling will not shirk

05:57.080 --> 05:58.710
any responsibility that we should bear.

05:58.740 --> 06:00.620
But don't forget—

06:00.810 --> 06:02.810
when the demons launched a full-scale attack

06:02.840 --> 06:04.520
and the Eternals suffered defeat after defeat,

06:05.060 --> 06:06.060
who was it

06:06.090 --> 06:08.590
that led his disciples back to the battlefield,

06:08.620 --> 06:09.810
turned the tide,

06:09.870 --> 06:11.000
and restored the Eternals'

06:11.000 --> 06:13.410
prestige and status in front of the demons?

06:13.590 --> 06:15.080
Lanling may have achieved victory in battle,

06:15.100 --> 06:16.780
but being great once doesn't mean you can be great forever.

06:16.810 --> 06:17.660
Still better than those of you

06:17.680 --> 06:19.320
who couldn't even win a fight!

06:19.360 --> 06:19.830
You...

06:19.850 --> 06:21.090
High Eternal Jing Lei,

06:21.120 --> 06:22.760
is Lanling trying to suppress others by force?

06:22.800 --> 06:23.720
You want a duel?

06:23.720 --> 06:24.730
I'll just use one hand.

06:24.760 --> 06:25.610
Is that enough?

06:25.630 --> 06:26.780
Or I won't use either hand!

06:26.810 --> 06:27.490
Enough!

06:29.370 --> 06:31.010
If we're really going to assign blame,

06:31.450 --> 06:32.840
everyone here

06:32.870 --> 06:35.350
should be blamed.

06:41.260 --> 06:42.590
Over the years,

06:42.620 --> 06:44.700
the 72 Sects have each kept to themselves,

06:44.720 --> 06:46.110
maintaining a facade of harmony.

06:46.130 --> 06:48.060
But when it mattered,

06:48.090 --> 06:49.970
everyone just looked out for their own interests.

06:50.010 --> 06:52.230
Every time, it was Lanling that stepped up first.

06:53.040 --> 06:54.210
If we hadn't

06:54.240 --> 06:56.090
only cared about our own survival,

06:56.110 --> 06:56.700
how would Jin Yao

06:56.750 --> 06:58.990
have had so many chances to commit crimes?

06:59.150 --> 07:00.070
That's right.

07:01.590 --> 07:02.640
Bei Chen.

07:03.850 --> 07:07.200
Don't be so disrespectful to your elders.

07:11.000 --> 07:12.240
I may be bold and rude,

07:12.260 --> 07:14.320
but I'm just saying the truth.

07:15.340 --> 07:16.730
Bei Chen is right.

07:16.760 --> 07:17.760
Nan Wan!

07:19.210 --> 07:20.650
Master, if you want to punish me,

07:20.670 --> 07:21.840
I'll accept it.

07:21.870 --> 07:23.870
But there are things I must say today.

07:23.900 --> 07:25.580
We Eternals exist

07:25.600 --> 07:27.360
to protect people and the world.

07:27.390 --> 07:29.120
But at some point,

07:29.230 --> 07:31.310
we became obsessed with fame and fortune,

07:31.360 --> 07:32.800
weighing gains and losses,

07:32.830 --> 07:33.730
taking credit but dodging blame,

07:33.760 --> 07:34.900
and seeking benefits while avoiding risks.

07:34.920 --> 07:36.310
I want to ask,

07:37.100 --> 07:39.780
are these still the Eternal Sects you once pledged yourselves to?

07:39.920 --> 07:41.720
What do you two young men know?

07:41.750 --> 07:42.680
Shut up!

07:43.300 --> 07:45.590
What we know comes from what we've seen.

07:45.680 --> 07:47.520
Back when Zhen Yu wreaked havoc in Ning'an City,

07:47.830 --> 07:50.510
Lanling sent word and asked for our help to fight Cold Spring.

07:50.540 --> 07:53.250
Yet all the sects made excuses to avoid the battle.

07:53.650 --> 07:55.300
Later, during the Wutong Contest,

07:56.030 --> 07:58.350
when Zhen Yu tried to kill Eternals and demons in the Outlanders' City,

07:58.370 --> 07:59.860
we still didn't dare to step in

07:59.880 --> 08:01.980
and let Zhen Yu grow unchecked step by step,

08:02.000 --> 08:03.920
causing more and more disasters.

08:04.830 --> 08:07.120
Now, Zhen Yu has taken the Hidden Heart

08:07.150 --> 08:08.340
and captured Chong Zhao.

08:08.360 --> 08:09.880
A calamity is coming!

08:10.530 --> 08:11.330
Do you all,

08:11.860 --> 08:13.490
as Eternals,

08:13.540 --> 08:16.300
really believe this is the fault of just one sect?

08:16.890 --> 08:17.620
He has a point.

08:17.640 --> 08:18.450
Indeed.

08:20.620 --> 08:21.790
He's right.

08:21.810 --> 08:23.040
They are right.

08:23.470 --> 08:26.510
If the 72 Sects could work together,

08:26.540 --> 08:27.690
be honest and open with each other,

08:27.710 --> 08:29.270
and move forward hand in hand,

08:29.300 --> 08:31.500
there wouldn't have been such grave mistakes.

08:32.730 --> 08:35.010
The Eternals are one family.

08:35.030 --> 08:37.490
Internal matters are trivial.

08:38.000 --> 08:40.000
The priority right now

08:40.020 --> 08:41.860
is to stop the return of the Hidden Lord.

08:41.960 --> 08:44.390
-Yes. Yes.
-Yes.

08:44.390 --> 08:45.840
-Yes.
-Yes.

09:03.510 --> 09:04.390
You're awake?

09:06.770 --> 09:07.580
Zhen Yu,

09:08.170 --> 09:09.650
what do you want to do?

09:09.680 --> 09:11.150
Haven't you already figured out

09:11.400 --> 09:13.760
what I want to do?

09:13.790 --> 09:15.900
You've known all along that I carry the Divine Mantle of the Hidden Lord.

09:15.930 --> 09:17.030
That's why you made me a demon

09:17.030 --> 09:18.390
and injected the Hidden power into me.

09:18.420 --> 09:20.070
You want to awaken Mo Li.

09:21.350 --> 09:22.000
That's right.

09:22.020 --> 09:23.530
I'm not him!

09:23.730 --> 09:24.720
I'm Chong Zhao,

09:24.720 --> 09:25.960
not that demon!

09:25.990 --> 09:27.890
You're the Hidden Lord.

09:27.910 --> 09:29.200
You've simply

09:29.230 --> 09:30.780
forgotten who you truly are.

09:31.630 --> 09:33.590
Now that the Demon Lord has returned,

09:33.610 --> 09:35.530
once he saves Bai Shuo's life,

09:35.560 --> 09:37.870
he'll undoubtedly find a way to destroy the Hidden Heart.

09:37.890 --> 09:39.490
I must bring back the Hidden Lord

09:39.520 --> 09:40.740
as soon as possible.

09:40.770 --> 09:42.010
The Hidden Heart is damaged.

09:42.440 --> 09:44.130
It's impossible to bring back Mo Li.

09:44.840 --> 09:46.230
Give it up.

09:46.250 --> 09:47.490
Give up?

09:48.360 --> 09:49.840
I've been planning this

09:49.880 --> 09:51.570
for 60,000 years.

09:51.770 --> 09:53.300
I will never give up.

09:53.900 --> 09:57.130
No one in this world can stop me

09:57.150 --> 09:58.960
from bringing him back.

10:07.960 --> 10:08.920
Chong Zhao.

10:10.660 --> 10:11.660
Xi.

10:15.070 --> 10:16.510
You escaped Cold Spring Palace

10:16.530 --> 10:18.050
in the chaos that day,

10:18.590 --> 10:20.860
but today, you've come back willingly to die.

10:22.300 --> 10:23.340
Good.

10:23.580 --> 10:26.150
I raised you for 10 years. It's time to repay that kindness.

10:26.170 --> 10:27.620
You raised me?

10:27.980 --> 10:30.590
Back then, you deceived me into leaving my family,

10:30.610 --> 10:32.320
turned me into a demon,

10:32.350 --> 10:33.030
and used me as your weapon

10:33.030 --> 10:34.060
for 10 whole years.

10:34.090 --> 10:35.900
How dare you call that kindness?

10:35.920 --> 10:38.040
No one can escape the blame for my father's death.

10:38.060 --> 10:39.060
I deserve to die,

10:39.210 --> 10:40.450
and you

10:40.540 --> 10:42.060
should pay with your life too!

10:42.080 --> 10:44.180
If you want someone to blame,

10:44.200 --> 10:45.720
blame that old turtle.

10:45.750 --> 10:46.940
Three children,

10:46.960 --> 10:49.090
one in the Bai family

10:49.110 --> 10:51.500
and one in the Bai Ze Clan.

10:51.950 --> 10:54.590
You had spiritual energy back then,

10:54.620 --> 10:55.780
while Bai Shuo

10:55.800 --> 10:57.400
seemed utterly ordinary.

10:57.430 --> 10:59.400
Anyone would have believed

10:59.420 --> 11:02.360
you were the one with Xing Yue's Divine Mantle.

11:03.260 --> 11:06.930
If not for the heavenly law that only a Supreme Deity can kill another Supreme Deity,

11:07.000 --> 11:09.030
I wouldn't have kept you

11:09.060 --> 11:10.180
and Chen Ye by my side.

11:11.040 --> 11:13.180
I was waiting for His Lordship's return

11:13.200 --> 11:14.900
to get rid of both of you.

11:14.970 --> 11:16.210
If I had known this,

11:16.230 --> 11:18.200
I would have killed you both a long time ago

11:18.230 --> 11:19.470
to prevent future trouble.

11:19.490 --> 11:21.010
One wrong step

11:21.040 --> 11:22.340
led to another.

11:22.690 --> 11:23.900
But luckily,

11:23.930 --> 11:26.810
it's not too late to fix everything now.

11:32.820 --> 11:34.180
How dare you hurt her?

11:34.210 --> 11:35.620
I'll kill you!

11:37.260 --> 11:39.420
Today, here,

11:39.450 --> 11:41.120
you won't need to kill me.

12:41.600 --> 12:44.000
You're actually using your own heart to mend the Hidden Heart.

12:44.030 --> 12:46.380
As long as I can bring His Lordship back,

12:46.400 --> 12:49.120
it's all worth it.

13:52.590 --> 13:54.380
It's been 60,000 years.

13:55.120 --> 13:57.700
I'm finally back.

13:58.260 --> 14:01.690
Welcome back, my lord.

14:01.710 --> 14:04.150
You gave your life to bring me back.

14:04.460 --> 14:05.620
Do you regret it?

14:06.070 --> 14:08.400
When nobody knew about me,

14:08.710 --> 14:10.590
I was nothing but

14:11.610 --> 14:13.840
a lonely, small snake,

14:14.160 --> 14:17.970
dying after being attacked by a pack of snakes on South Mountain.

14:18.000 --> 14:20.690
It was you, my lord, who saved me.

14:20.720 --> 14:25.110
My life was yours

14:25.630 --> 14:27.130
to begin with.

14:27.450 --> 14:28.970
Now that…

14:28.990 --> 14:31.460
I've brought you back,

14:31.540 --> 14:33.070
I

14:33.700 --> 14:35.770
have no regrets.

14:36.360 --> 14:37.630
Rest assured.

14:38.230 --> 14:40.310
Those who killed you

14:40.360 --> 14:42.260
and betrayed me,

14:42.290 --> 14:44.610
I won't let go of any of them!

14:46.280 --> 14:49.000
There were things left unfinished 60,000 years ago.

14:49.500 --> 14:51.070
It's time

14:51.170 --> 14:53.650
to finish them now.

15:25.690 --> 15:27.540
You're Bai Xi,

15:28.190 --> 15:31.080
the elder sister of Xing Yue in this life,

15:31.280 --> 15:33.820
and the one Chong Zhao loves.

15:59.790 --> 16:01.200
The sky looks eerie.

16:01.230 --> 16:02.630
The Hidden Lord has returned.

16:04.760 --> 16:06.120
How could Zhen Yu have repaired

16:06.120 --> 16:07.520
the damaged Hidden Heart so quickly?

16:07.600 --> 16:08.670
A great calamity has come,

16:08.690 --> 16:09.810
and there's no avoiding it.

16:09.840 --> 16:11.080
Since we can't escape,

16:11.100 --> 16:12.440
we have to face it.

16:14.080 --> 16:15.160
Sect Leaders,

16:15.690 --> 16:17.510
please return at once

16:17.530 --> 16:19.730
and protect your disciples and the humans.

16:20.040 --> 16:22.580
Be ready to fight to save the world.

16:22.610 --> 16:23.720
Don't worry, High Eternal.

16:23.740 --> 16:25.320
Though the Eternals have been divided for years,

16:25.340 --> 16:26.760
we know where to stand

16:26.780 --> 16:27.730
when it truly matters.

16:28.290 --> 16:29.570
We'll head back now

16:29.680 --> 16:30.730
and stay ready.

16:34.980 --> 16:36.910
Take care.

16:37.170 --> 16:38.300
You too.

16:45.440 --> 16:46.930
Do you think

16:47.340 --> 16:49.380
we'll survive this catastrophe?

16:49.720 --> 16:51.360
The road ahead is unclear,

16:51.390 --> 16:52.790
but no matter what,

16:53.770 --> 16:55.690
we'll stand firm until the very end.

17:06.490 --> 17:07.910
He's back.

17:25.800 --> 17:26.670
-You're awake.
-You're back.

17:26.690 --> 17:27.780
-Xing Yue.
-Fan Yue.

17:47.050 --> 17:48.130
The Demon Lord,

17:48.700 --> 17:50.100
Jing Yuan?

17:55.840 --> 17:57.040
60,000 years ago,

17:57.060 --> 17:59.180
I used the divine power of the Demon Lord to bind the Hidden Heart.

17:59.210 --> 18:00.640
Today, when the Contemplation Stone was shattered

18:00.660 --> 18:01.830
and the Hidden Heart was damaged,

18:01.860 --> 18:03.540
my divine power returned to me,

18:03.560 --> 18:04.730
so I woke up.

18:05.480 --> 18:06.610
What about Fan Yue?

18:07.000 --> 18:08.870
You hope the one who woke up

18:08.900 --> 18:09.710
was him?

18:15.990 --> 18:17.680
Xi and Chong Zhao

18:17.710 --> 18:18.820
are in danger.

18:18.900 --> 18:19.870
It's too late.

18:20.620 --> 18:21.900
Mo Li has already returned.

18:26.190 --> 18:28.110
Even if the Hidden Lord has come back,

18:28.150 --> 18:29.390
Xi is still there.

18:29.410 --> 18:30.640
I need to save her.

18:30.660 --> 18:32.500
Mo Li and I are evenly matched in power.

18:32.520 --> 18:33.630
We can't defeat each other.

18:33.860 --> 18:35.550
Mo Li knows this as well.

18:35.580 --> 18:36.590
That's why he hasn't made a move

18:36.590 --> 18:38.110
against Bright Moon Palace yet.

18:38.610 --> 18:39.740
But the same

18:39.760 --> 18:41.080
goes for me.

18:41.110 --> 18:42.510
Without the Xing Yue Divine Bow,

18:42.530 --> 18:43.870
we can't kill Mo Li,

18:44.010 --> 18:45.420
destroy the Hidden Heart,

18:45.530 --> 18:46.700
or save anyone.

18:47.060 --> 18:48.300
We can't win,

18:48.820 --> 18:50.320
so we'll just do nothing?

18:50.420 --> 18:51.990
You've met Xiu Yan,

18:52.010 --> 18:53.090
so you should know

18:53.120 --> 18:54.900
if you want to save your sister,

18:54.920 --> 18:56.530
wake Chong Zhao up,

18:56.560 --> 18:58.320
and save this world,

18:58.340 --> 19:00.340
you have to find the Xing Yue Divine Bow first.

19:00.360 --> 19:01.670
It's the only way.

19:02.440 --> 19:03.570
Don't worry too much.

19:03.820 --> 19:04.750
I'm here.

19:05.540 --> 19:07.230
We faced this together 60,000 years ago,

19:07.670 --> 19:08.870
and we'll face it together now.

19:09.710 --> 19:11.760
60,000 years ago, the one by your side

19:12.770 --> 19:13.730
was Xing Yue.

19:18.170 --> 19:19.460
You are Xing Yue.

19:26.630 --> 19:28.570
But I'm Bai Shuo.

19:53.230 --> 19:54.380
Chong Zhao.

19:56.990 --> 19:58.780
You truly love him.

19:58.860 --> 20:01.410
The first thing you do upon waking up is call out his name.

20:04.850 --> 20:06.020
You're not Chong Zhao.

20:09.400 --> 20:11.400
You can tell right away.

20:12.350 --> 20:14.660
You do know him well.

20:15.090 --> 20:16.610
Where is Chong Zhao?

20:16.720 --> 20:18.040
What have you done to him?

20:18.790 --> 20:20.100
He's still here,

20:20.130 --> 20:22.820
kept in the deepest part of the sea of consciousness.

20:22.840 --> 20:23.760
Let him go!

20:25.240 --> 20:27.020
And if I don't?

20:32.120 --> 20:33.920
Perhaps you don't know this—

20:33.940 --> 20:34.970
this body of his

20:35.030 --> 20:36.790
was created for me to begin with.

20:36.820 --> 20:38.650
It's his honor

20:38.670 --> 20:40.280
that I'm using it now.

20:41.820 --> 20:43.180
As for you,

20:45.620 --> 20:48.310
if you don't want Chong Zhao to completely disappear,

20:49.340 --> 20:51.340
you'd better stay right here.

20:51.970 --> 20:53.600
Why…

20:53.620 --> 20:55.040
why don't you just kill me?

20:55.600 --> 20:57.770
You're Xing Yue's sister.

20:57.800 --> 20:59.040
If I kill you,

20:59.780 --> 21:01.220
she'll be angry.

21:06.980 --> 21:08.100
Remember,

21:08.140 --> 21:09.980
I don't like noise.

21:10.210 --> 21:12.290
Don't run around. Don't make a fuss.

21:12.310 --> 21:13.640
Stay quiet.

21:38.640 --> 21:40.680
After 60,000 years,

21:40.710 --> 21:42.750
the auras of Eternals and demons on the Eastern Continent

21:42.770 --> 21:44.720
have grown much stronger.

21:44.920 --> 21:46.770
Mo Li, what are you going to do?

21:49.900 --> 21:52.660
Zhen Yu waited for me for 60,000 years.

21:52.680 --> 21:55.450
Shouldn't someone accompany him in death?

21:55.860 --> 21:59.020
The Eternals and demons will join forces to kill you.

22:01.030 --> 22:02.680
It seems you still don't understand

22:02.750 --> 22:04.400
how powerful a deity is.

22:04.420 --> 22:05.920
To Eternals and demons, humans are nothing

22:05.920 --> 22:07.350
more than insignificant ants.

22:07.370 --> 22:09.250
And to me, Eternals and demons

22:09.740 --> 22:11.530
are just insignificant ants too.

22:12.000 --> 22:13.550
Even if you don't fear Eternals and demons,

22:13.630 --> 22:15.220
the Demon Lord has returned,

22:15.240 --> 22:16.400
and he won't let you

22:16.400 --> 22:17.830
get anything you want.

22:29.740 --> 22:32.460
Jing Yuan's divine power originates from the Purple Moon,

22:32.710 --> 22:35.540
and Xing Yue's divine power originates from the stars.

22:35.570 --> 22:37.390
Do you know why my divine power originates from

22:37.410 --> 22:39.170
this ancient mirror?

22:39.740 --> 22:41.660
The Purple Moon and the stars illuminate the world,

22:41.690 --> 22:42.930
seemingly vast and far-reaching.

22:43.580 --> 22:45.830
This Divine Mirror, the size of a plate,

22:45.860 --> 22:47.300
seems too small.

22:47.320 --> 22:48.670
But that's far from the truth.

22:49.060 --> 22:51.060
The Heavenly Divine Mirror

22:51.080 --> 22:52.870
reflects the whole world.

22:52.900 --> 22:54.360
In terms of vastness,

22:54.610 --> 22:57.250
there is a whole world in the Divine Mirror.

22:57.280 --> 22:59.000
That's truly vastness!

22:59.500 --> 23:02.180
With the power of the entire world as my source,

23:02.210 --> 23:03.700
what do I have to fear?

23:03.940 --> 23:06.110
As long as I absorb enough power from the Eternals and demons,

23:06.140 --> 23:08.490
no one will be able to stop me!

23:54.030 --> 23:55.470
Stop!

24:02.120 --> 24:04.210
Do you really think you can

24:04.230 --> 24:06.670
break the restraints of the Hidden Race's Supreme Deity?

24:06.700 --> 24:07.960
If you're so powerful,

24:07.980 --> 24:09.740
why do you bother imprisoning me here?

24:14.220 --> 24:16.330
You've trapped me here

24:16.360 --> 24:18.240
because you can't kill me either.

24:18.590 --> 24:21.150
After all, this body belonged to me,

24:21.180 --> 24:23.530
and you've just borrowed it to return.

24:23.660 --> 24:25.250
If you kill me,

24:25.270 --> 24:26.580
you'll hurt yourself.

24:30.640 --> 24:32.690
You're too noisy.

24:41.040 --> 24:43.280
Much quieter now.

24:48.930 --> 24:50.000
Tian Huo,

24:50.700 --> 24:52.180
you've finally returned.

24:58.300 --> 24:58.900
He...

24:58.930 --> 25:00.000
I've already heard.

25:00.330 --> 25:01.540
Other demons told me.

25:03.510 --> 25:04.960
The Demon Lord, Jing Yuan,

25:05.710 --> 25:07.330
has returned.

25:08.670 --> 25:09.760
During this trip,

25:09.780 --> 25:11.230
I uncovered some things.

25:11.810 --> 25:12.850
I searched all the sects and clans

25:12.870 --> 25:14.780
of Eternals, demons, and humans

25:14.830 --> 25:15.880
but found nothing.

25:15.920 --> 25:17.750
In the end, I found a clue in the Eastern Sea.

25:18.890 --> 25:20.710
According to ancient records there,

25:20.740 --> 25:22.490
when the Divine Region collapsed,

25:22.530 --> 25:24.540
several pieces of meteoric iron fell from the sky,

25:24.560 --> 25:26.510
scattering along the shores of the Eastern Sea.

25:26.540 --> 25:28.980
The Eastern Sea… Meteoric iron?

25:30.150 --> 25:31.630
I remember you once said

25:31.650 --> 25:33.380
the Outlander King's Sword was forged by the first King of Outlanders

25:33.410 --> 25:35.520
using meteoric iron found by the Eastern Sea.

25:35.550 --> 25:36.700
That's right.

25:36.720 --> 25:38.090
I returned to the Outlanders' City,

25:38.120 --> 25:40.040
scoured records from 1,000 years ago,

25:40.070 --> 25:42.450
and finally found the original form of the meteoric iron from back then.

25:45.930 --> 25:46.790
It seems the Xing Yue Arrow

25:46.790 --> 25:48.470
was already fractured and melted

25:48.500 --> 25:50.230
when it fell from the Divine Region,

25:50.820 --> 25:52.400
losing its original form.

25:52.790 --> 25:54.720
No wonder it remained undiscovered for so long.

25:55.190 --> 25:58.000
So the Outlander King's Sword is the Xing Yue Arrow.

25:58.400 --> 25:59.430
What about the Xing Yue Divine Bow?

25:59.450 --> 26:00.180
Any clues?

26:00.860 --> 26:01.790
Not yet.

26:04.050 --> 26:04.850
Report!

26:06.210 --> 26:07.490
Bad news!

26:07.530 --> 26:08.450
The Hidden Lord, Mo Li,

26:08.510 --> 26:10.270
used the Heavenly Divine Mirror to absorb power from countless Eternals and demons.

26:10.270 --> 26:11.770
Lanling issued a proclamation to rally against the Hidden Lord

26:11.800 --> 26:12.880
but was attacked by him instead.

26:12.900 --> 26:14.060
The four High Eternals of Lanling

26:14.090 --> 26:15.360
have been taken to Cold Spring Palace.

26:25.180 --> 26:27.720
It's your first time in Cold Spring Palace, right?

26:28.590 --> 26:31.130
Lanling always boasts about protecting the world

26:31.200 --> 26:32.480
and defending justice against evil.

26:32.520 --> 26:33.480
Yet Cold Spring Palace,

26:33.480 --> 26:36.030
a place steeped in wickedness and cruelty,

26:36.030 --> 26:38.550
has stood untouched by you for all these years.

26:39.220 --> 26:41.690
Instead, you let Chong Zhao become a demon to infiltrate it.

26:41.920 --> 26:43.770
How ridiculous.

26:43.800 --> 26:44.990
It is ridiculous.

26:45.010 --> 26:47.490
The head disciple of Lanling turns out to be the Hidden Lord.

26:47.520 --> 26:48.670
I said before,

26:48.690 --> 26:50.580
if Chong Zhao truly becomes the Hidden Lord,

26:50.610 --> 26:52.170
I'll kill you

26:52.200 --> 26:53.310
even if it costs me my life!

26:53.990 --> 26:54.910
Kill me?

26:59.540 --> 27:00.270
Jing Lei!

27:00.270 --> 27:01.400
-Jing Lei!
-Senior.

27:02.090 --> 27:05.050
I hate fools who overestimate themselves the most.

27:05.140 --> 27:07.980
What you're doing is against Heaven.

27:08.100 --> 27:10.180
If I can't stop you,

27:10.200 --> 27:11.980
someone else will.

27:14.510 --> 27:15.580
Still so delusional

27:17.220 --> 27:19.530
even in the face of death.

27:19.550 --> 27:21.390
Chong Zhao, wake up!

27:21.410 --> 27:23.380
He's your Uncle Jing Lei!

27:32.220 --> 27:33.500
Jing Lei!

27:34.870 --> 27:36.070
Senior!

27:36.090 --> 27:37.720
Jing Lei!

27:49.250 --> 27:51.360
Enough of your fantasies.

27:51.380 --> 27:53.030
I'm not Chong Zhao.

27:53.060 --> 27:55.060
Even if you kill us all,

27:55.080 --> 27:56.100
you still won't be able to kill

27:56.160 --> 27:57.950
Xing Yue or Jing Yuan!

27:57.980 --> 28:00.170
You returned at the same time.

28:00.190 --> 28:03.540
It shows Heaven's constraints on you!

28:03.660 --> 28:04.800
Is that so?

28:05.080 --> 28:06.990
Without the Xing Yue Divine Bow,

28:07.010 --> 28:10.000
they're no threat to me.

28:10.030 --> 28:12.350
I'll show you

28:12.370 --> 28:14.720
how they'll pay the price for everything they did

28:14.750 --> 28:16.270
in the past!

28:50.580 --> 28:52.610
You actually managed to wound me.

28:53.010 --> 28:54.640
It seems you're indeed not ordinary.

28:55.630 --> 28:57.160
I spared your life,

28:57.190 --> 28:59.300
and yet you tried to kill me.

28:59.380 --> 29:02.490
Is this what you and Chong Zhao call true love?

29:03.110 --> 29:04.670
You demon,

29:04.690 --> 29:05.890
you don't deserve to mention his name!

29:06.080 --> 29:07.200
If not for me,

29:07.200 --> 29:09.200
Chong Zhao wouldn't even exist in this world.

29:09.220 --> 29:10.700
You should thank me

29:10.750 --> 29:13.120
for giving you the chance to meet him,

29:13.180 --> 29:14.420
shouldn't you?

29:17.920 --> 29:20.310
If you're going to kill me, then do it.

29:20.340 --> 29:22.360
Stop disgusting me with Chong Zhao's face.

29:22.380 --> 29:23.920
He's nothing like you.

29:23.950 --> 29:25.580
He's loyal and righteous,

29:25.600 --> 29:26.490
unlike you—

29:26.580 --> 29:28.690
your hands are stained with the blood of your fellow disciples!

29:28.720 --> 29:29.890
Fellow disciples?

29:34.000 --> 29:37.150
The people of Lanling are nothing to me.

29:37.170 --> 29:39.910
Have you killed fewer Eternals than I have?

29:40.310 --> 29:41.790
Do you really think

29:41.820 --> 29:42.950
just because you want to be kind,

29:43.000 --> 29:45.400
your bloody past can be erased

29:45.400 --> 29:46.880
and your sins can be forgiven?

29:47.290 --> 29:48.840
Lady Fu Ling.

29:55.290 --> 29:57.690
Do you remember what you said to Chong Zhao

29:57.710 --> 29:59.740
when you brought him to Cold Spring Palace?

30:02.240 --> 30:03.750
You said you were in hell

30:03.750 --> 30:05.110
and wanted him to stay with you.

30:06.860 --> 30:08.450
You've gotten your wish now.

30:08.480 --> 30:10.770
And I can promise you this—

30:10.800 --> 30:13.180
you and Chong Zhao will stay in hell forever,

30:13.270 --> 30:14.920
never to see the light of day.

30:15.920 --> 30:17.600
You know everything

30:17.700 --> 30:19.130
about Chong Zhao?

30:23.290 --> 30:24.180
Yes.

30:24.330 --> 30:26.230
And it only confirms that he's a loser.

30:26.660 --> 30:29.050
He talks endlessly about justice,

30:29.130 --> 30:30.960
but he doesn't understand

30:31.300 --> 30:33.910
that evil is the true nature of this world.

30:44.770 --> 30:47.320
Go ahead, keep trying to kill me,

30:47.390 --> 30:49.300
if you think you can succeed.

30:57.370 --> 30:59.190
You're keeping someone

30:59.220 --> 31:01.180
who wants to kill you by your side.

31:01.390 --> 31:03.000
Are you really that confident,

31:03.020 --> 31:04.420
or do you have some ulterior motive?

31:04.440 --> 31:06.520
The unfinished business from 60,000 years ago

31:06.600 --> 31:08.630
isn't just ruling the world.

31:08.650 --> 31:10.470
It's also marrying Xing Yue.

31:10.640 --> 31:12.050
In this whole world,

31:14.120 --> 31:15.280
you

31:15.300 --> 31:16.970
are the perfect witness for this union,

31:18.390 --> 31:19.540
aren't you?

32:16.130 --> 32:18.170
Are you planning to ruin your hands

32:18.220 --> 32:19.990
before you shoot Mo Li?

32:36.060 --> 32:37.640
It's just a small injury.

32:38.810 --> 32:39.980
I can handle it myself.

32:41.610 --> 32:43.570
When I learned martial arts from my father,

32:43.590 --> 32:45.110
among all martial skills,

32:45.140 --> 32:47.360
I was never really interested in archery

32:47.980 --> 32:49.550
and hardly practiced it growing up.

32:50.360 --> 32:52.160
Who would've thought that one day,

32:52.180 --> 32:54.290
I'd have to rely on a Divine Bow to kill my enemy?

32:54.320 --> 32:56.630
I just want to hone my archery

32:56.650 --> 32:57.890
before we find the Divine Bow.

32:57.920 --> 33:00.470
The Bow and you are in perfect harmony.

33:00.500 --> 33:01.780
Where the heart points,

33:01.800 --> 33:03.230
the arrow will follow.

33:03.260 --> 33:05.110
You don't need practice to hit your mark every time.

33:06.830 --> 33:08.860
Someone once told me,

33:08.920 --> 33:10.850
it's not easy to defeat the strong

33:10.880 --> 33:12.230
when you're weak.

33:12.250 --> 33:13.650
Besides learning the tricks,

33:13.680 --> 33:15.420
you also need relentless training.

33:15.470 --> 33:17.510
I'm not gifted,

33:17.540 --> 33:19.570
and now I've lost the power of the Five Contemplations.

33:19.590 --> 33:20.970
To be safe,

33:21.510 --> 33:23.520
it's better to practice hard.

33:23.620 --> 33:24.660
Practice is fine,

33:25.410 --> 33:26.850
but don't push yourself too hard.

33:31.740 --> 33:32.960
Thank you.

33:33.150 --> 33:34.720
Why are you thanking me all of a sudden?

33:34.740 --> 33:36.790
10 years ago, on the night of the Lantern Festival,

33:36.950 --> 33:38.930
you saved Xi and me.

33:39.320 --> 33:40.940
I've spent the last 10 years seeking immortality,

33:40.990 --> 33:42.600
just so I could repay you.

33:42.900 --> 33:44.190
There's no need for thanks

33:44.220 --> 33:45.540
and even less need for repayment.

33:45.560 --> 33:46.670
It's almost laughable.

33:47.170 --> 33:48.860
When I saved you that night,

33:48.890 --> 33:50.970
I didn't know you carried Xing Yue's Divine Mantle.

33:54.260 --> 33:55.960
Not all immortals pity mortals.

33:57.380 --> 33:58.790
You're lucky

33:59.630 --> 34:01.600
to have eyes resembling hers.

34:02.820 --> 34:04.930
But if I had recognized you that day,

34:05.170 --> 34:06.200
perhaps things wouldn't have...

34:06.200 --> 34:07.720
Actually, I've always wondered something.

34:08.739 --> 34:11.050
60,000 years ago, the Divine Region collapsed,

34:11.070 --> 34:12.389
and all deities died.

34:12.420 --> 34:15.190
So why were you still in this world 10 years ago?

34:15.210 --> 34:16.770
My physical body was indeed destroyed

34:16.800 --> 34:18.320
60,000 years ago,

34:18.340 --> 34:20.440
but the Divine Mantles of the three Supreme Deities never perish.

34:20.500 --> 34:21.710
I was so desperate to find Xing Yue

34:21.739 --> 34:23.739
that I forcibly tore apart my Divine Mantle.

34:23.760 --> 34:25.030
Half of it went to Bai Ze,

34:25.060 --> 34:26.909
and the other half stayed in the world, continuing the search,

34:26.929 --> 34:28.949
until the 15-year-old Fan Yue accidentally fell off a cliff,

34:28.980 --> 34:30.500
forcing the two halves of my Divine Mantle to reunite.

34:30.580 --> 34:32.020
Only then did I enter his body,

34:32.040 --> 34:33.650
but the shock of the reunion caused me to lose my memory.

34:33.679 --> 34:35.320
You tore apart your Divine Mantle,

34:35.830 --> 34:37.440
wandered the world alone,

34:38.699 --> 34:40.489
and searched for her like that

34:40.510 --> 34:41.580
for 60,000 years?

34:42.239 --> 34:43.429
Her?

34:45.460 --> 34:47.190
Why not say I was searching for you?

34:49.920 --> 34:51.130
You are her.

34:53.790 --> 34:55.270
Perhaps you haven't noticed it.

34:55.500 --> 34:58.460
Other than the moment I awoke, when you called me Xing Yue,

34:58.490 --> 35:00.450
you haven't called me my name since.

35:00.470 --> 35:01.910
Is it because you think it's unnecessary,

35:01.940 --> 35:03.270
because you're avoiding it,

35:04.040 --> 35:05.080
or because…

35:05.730 --> 35:08.090
you yourself haven't figured out

35:08.110 --> 35:09.790
who I am now?

35:14.920 --> 35:16.440
You're right.

35:16.840 --> 35:18.840
I can't let myself collapse

35:18.860 --> 35:20.340
before I defeat the Hidden Lord.

35:21.700 --> 35:23.100
I'm going back.

35:23.120 --> 35:24.550
You should get some rest too.

35:56.630 --> 35:58.630
Under the stars tonight,

35:59.360 --> 36:00.880
with friends and loved ones by our side,

36:01.630 --> 36:05.070
and the ten thousand miles of the Polar Region as our witness,

36:05.480 --> 36:06.480
Fan Yue,

36:07.730 --> 36:09.510
will you marry me?

36:10.490 --> 36:11.970
Side by side in the heavens;

36:13.980 --> 36:15.420
bound together on earth.

36:16.670 --> 36:18.110
Two hearts as one,

36:19.830 --> 36:21.120
unchanging for all eternity.

36:22.000 --> 36:23.570
You've accepted my flowers,

36:24.040 --> 36:25.920
so you're mine now.

36:25.940 --> 36:26.750
Okay.

36:29.710 --> 36:30.750
Fan Yue,

36:31.230 --> 36:33.150
you share the same Divine Mantle,

36:33.180 --> 36:34.690
the same body,

36:35.130 --> 36:36.330
and the same face.

36:37.270 --> 36:39.060
But does that really make him you?

36:40.960 --> 36:41.960
Master has returned.

36:41.980 --> 36:43.190
You should be happy.

36:43.730 --> 36:44.790
But you seem…

36:47.290 --> 36:48.810
Are you struggling with

36:48.830 --> 36:50.760
whether to see him as Master

36:50.790 --> 36:51.940
or the Demon Lord?

36:54.180 --> 36:55.110
What about you?

36:56.300 --> 36:58.450
To me, Master just has

36:58.470 --> 37:00.190
the memories of the Demon Lord now.

37:00.920 --> 37:02.000
He's just stronger

37:02.020 --> 37:03.580
and colder.

37:03.610 --> 37:04.570
In my eyes,

37:04.590 --> 37:06.510
he's both my master and the Demon Lord.

37:06.890 --> 37:07.920
But this version of him

37:07.920 --> 37:09.900
means different things to me than to you.

37:09.920 --> 37:11.650
I thought I could do it.

37:12.850 --> 37:14.700
I thought I could see him as Fan Yue.

37:16.660 --> 37:18.290
But it turns out that some feelings

37:18.320 --> 37:19.650
just can't coexist.

37:21.580 --> 37:23.490
I have the Divine Mantle of Xing Yue,

37:23.520 --> 37:25.250
and I've learned Xing Yue's life story

37:25.280 --> 37:27.030
in the Lunar Hidden Sea.

37:27.050 --> 37:28.770
But in the end, I am Bai Shuo,

37:29.250 --> 37:30.400
not Xing Yue.

37:30.850 --> 37:32.440
I didn't spend those long centuries

37:32.470 --> 37:34.620
with Jing Yuan in the Divine Region,

37:35.240 --> 37:36.880
nor did I share with him

37:36.900 --> 37:39.050
the joy and sorrow of those days

37:39.080 --> 37:40.880
and all those life-and-death situations.

37:41.350 --> 37:43.260
The one who lived through everything with me

37:44.180 --> 37:45.780
and faced death with me

37:47.280 --> 37:48.430
was Fan Yue.

37:50.040 --> 37:51.090
Then,

37:51.110 --> 37:52.480
what are you going to do?

37:52.930 --> 37:54.850
He's the Demon Lord,

37:54.870 --> 37:56.390
but he's also Master.

37:58.300 --> 37:59.460
I don't know.

38:01.990 --> 38:02.950
Tian Huo,

38:03.890 --> 38:06.060
can you leave me alone for a while?

38:28.240 --> 38:30.150
Looking at the stars in the night sky,

38:30.860 --> 38:32.140
what do you feel?

38:36.740 --> 38:38.260
The stars shine,

38:38.290 --> 38:39.570
illuminating the world

38:39.880 --> 38:40.970
and guiding the people.

38:42.810 --> 38:45.290
What you see is a sky full of stars,

38:45.320 --> 38:46.600
but to me,

38:46.830 --> 38:48.910
every single star in the sky

38:49.220 --> 38:50.990
is a reflection of Xing Yue.

38:52.040 --> 38:53.350
Bai Shuo was right.

38:53.910 --> 38:56.030
I've been deliberately avoiding it

38:56.280 --> 38:57.830
because I really,

38:59.150 --> 39:01.290
really want to see her as Xing Yue.

39:02.080 --> 39:03.260
So,

39:03.370 --> 39:04.530
you're finally admitting it.

39:04.890 --> 39:06.300
Bai Shuo is Bai Shuo,

39:06.590 --> 39:07.940
and Xing Yue is Xing Yue.

39:09.310 --> 39:11.640
Actually, I know everything between you and Bai Shuo;

39:12.110 --> 39:13.490
just like in the Outlanders' City,

39:13.800 --> 39:16.110
you knew everything between Mu and Bai Shuo.

39:16.580 --> 39:18.050
Why bring up Mu again?

39:19.400 --> 39:21.510
I just think the situations are similar.

39:21.970 --> 39:23.850
It seems you really don't like him.

39:25.180 --> 39:27.060
Just like you don't like me.

39:27.080 --> 39:28.520
We have the same Divine Mantle.

39:28.550 --> 39:29.760
I can feel it.

39:30.110 --> 39:31.430
You're angry with me too.

39:32.850 --> 39:34.300
Of course I am.

39:34.970 --> 39:36.140
Without you,

39:36.330 --> 39:37.880
she wouldn't have to make a choice.

39:38.770 --> 39:40.340
But if you didn't exist,

39:40.530 --> 39:42.440
Bai Shuo might already be dead,

39:42.780 --> 39:44.740
my Divine Mantle wouldn't have awakened,

39:45.410 --> 39:47.220
and this reunion wouldn't have been possible.

39:48.790 --> 39:50.670
You don't truly hate Mu,

39:51.440 --> 39:53.160
and I don't see you as an enemy either.

39:54.000 --> 39:55.560
On the contrary, I should thank you.

39:58.830 --> 39:59.690
Fan Yue,

40:00.090 --> 40:01.370
thank you for existing.

40:02.340 --> 40:04.510
Thank you for protecting her all this time.

40:07.330 --> 40:08.970
I protect her because I love her.

40:09.070 --> 40:10.190
I don't need your thanks.

40:11.810 --> 40:12.690
Yes,

40:13.660 --> 40:15.180
you love Bai Shuo,

40:15.860 --> 40:17.230
and I love Xing Yue.

40:18.100 --> 40:20.230
Only when the right people meet at the right time

40:20.590 --> 40:22.150
can they be together forever.

40:23.160 --> 40:24.450
Once things are out of alignment,

40:24.750 --> 40:26.190
everything falls apart.

40:29.250 --> 40:30.740
I spent 60,000 years

40:30.760 --> 40:32.150
searching for Xing Yue,

40:32.920 --> 40:34.330
but only now do I realize that

40:34.910 --> 40:36.100
Xing Yue, the Night Lord,

40:36.700 --> 40:38.260
is long gone.

40:39.040 --> 40:40.360
Then Jing Yuan, the Demon Lord,

40:41.830 --> 40:44.290
has no reason to stay in this world.

40:45.020 --> 40:46.800
Have you thought it through?

40:46.830 --> 40:48.310
Being able to see her one last time,

40:49.170 --> 40:50.770
I'm content.

40:52.650 --> 40:54.130
Perhaps my awakening

40:55.260 --> 40:57.900
was meant to bring you two together after 60,000 years.

40:58.970 --> 41:00.860
I'll leave my power to you

41:01.020 --> 41:03.150
and return Fan Yue to Bai Shuo.

41:03.820 --> 41:06.230
From now on, the Demon Lord Jing Yuan will no longer exist in this world.

41:06.320 --> 41:08.390
There will only be the Demon Lord Fan Yue.

41:08.870 --> 41:10.080
Promise me,

41:10.580 --> 41:11.950
keep her safe.

41:12.580 --> 41:14.150
Don't let the regrets between Xing Yue and me

41:14.200 --> 41:16.340
fall upon you and Bai Shuo.

41:38.220 --> 41:40.500
The stars are so beautiful tonight.

41:41.670 --> 41:42.570
Xing Yue,

41:43.770 --> 41:45.600
I'm coming to find you.

42:14.630 --> 42:15.570
Bai Shuo.

42:32.750 --> 42:36.380
♫The person standing far away♫

42:37.160 --> 42:39.430
♫Don't be afraid♫

42:40.060 --> 42:44.170
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

42:45.030 --> 42:51.650
♫Walk towards me♫

42:53.470 --> 42:56.540
♫My heart feels so...♫

42:57.180 --> 42:59.870
♫It's pounding♫

43:01.020 --> 43:01.830
Shuo.

43:03.630 --> 43:04.870
You're back.

43:05.180 --> 43:06.010
Yes.

43:07.120 --> 43:08.200
I'm back.

43:11.100 --> 43:15.040
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

43:18.800 --> 43:21.990
♫You are my distant call♫

43:22.790 --> 43:27.020
♫You are my first and last♫

43:27.760 --> 43:33.640
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

43:33.980 --> 43:37.000
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

43:37.650 --> 43:41.740
♫Let's never let go♫

43:46.230 --> 43:47.510
You're finally back.

43:48.380 --> 43:49.540
What about him?

43:49.570 --> 43:50.880
He's gone.

43:50.940 --> 43:52.980
He's headed to the starry sky

43:53.100 --> 43:54.900
to search for the one he loves.

43:56.880 --> 43:58.630
Will he find Xing Yue?

44:02.950 --> 44:04.610
Among the eternal, dazzling stars,

44:05.040 --> 44:06.480
none of them are her,

44:06.610 --> 44:08.210
yet all of them are her.

44:09.360 --> 44:11.630
He'll surely find his Xing Yue

44:11.740 --> 44:13.100
in another way.

44:19.170 --> 44:24.430
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

44:27.070 --> 44:30.670
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

44:31.210 --> 44:35.780
♫You are my determined way home♫

44:36.070 --> 44:41.760
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

44:42.280 --> 44:46.100
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫
